180
00:16:24,519 --> 00:16:25,240
Greetings, Zhen.

181
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:25,720
Hmm.

182
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,399
Are you trying to take my woman from me?

183
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,080
Yes, I am.

184
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,320
You think you deserve Zhao Chunman?

185
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,399
I don't,

186
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,720
but do you?

187
00:17:02,879 --> 00:17:04,319
Pick one. Her or me?

188
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:10,599
Zhou Chi, if you leave this place today,

189
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:11,880
don't ever come back.

190
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:15,400
I never look back.

191
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:25,960
Zhou Chi!

192
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:51,319
Anyone who stands in my way today dies.

193
00:17:53,799 --> 00:17:54,599
Out of my way!

194
00:17:55,519 --> 00:17:56,319
Let him go.

195
