♪Who promised whom♪

201
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:53,780
♪Who escaped with whom♪

202
00:18:54,900 --> 00:19:00,060
♪The vortex
that confuses time and space♪

203
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:07,340
♪Looking back at you and me♪

204
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:16,260
♪I'm looking for your dream♪

205
